{"tid":2034923,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[官方突發] 英足總決定腰斬19-20賽季超級聯賽","createTime":"2020-05-25T14:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T01:20:09.000Z","uid":59491,"like":8,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"61396abdb51573ee400bbb678f8b3682c1b293aa","tid":2034923,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:11:19.000Z","msg":"The FA Women&rsquo;s Super League &amp; Women&rsquo;s Championship Board has today <span style=\"color: red;\">confirmed the decision to end the 2019-20 season for the Barclays FA Women&rsquo;s Super League</span> and the FA Women&rsquo;s Championship, with immediate effect.<br />\n<br />\nFollowing full and thorough consultation with the clubs, the FA Women&rsquo;s Super League &amp; Women&rsquo;s Championship Board has discussed various recommendations which will be sent to the FA Board to determine the most appropriate sporting outcome for the 2019-20 season.<br />\n<br />\nThis will include identifying the entries for the 2020-21 UEFA Women&rsquo;s Champions League, which would be based on sporting merit from the 2019-20 Barclays FA Women&rsquo;s Super League season."},{"pid":"5735573f664f704efe7afee0f6d0aef894bf370e","tid":2034923,"uid":57035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:13:23.000Z","msg":"報左警"},{"pid":"eaf5ccd1c3e79b92b773aa1ed15c05350f72719a","tid":2034923,"uid":132488,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:18:25.000Z","msg":"猁: 停女超聯一定係死獌狗"},{"pid":"7a71dcb31bc33a7c1c402503d4edcd3ed094e98c","tid":2034923,"uid":202348,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:33:41.000Z","msg":"如果停女唔停男即係歧視我哋女人"},{"pid":"b30d24170c42c99dbab8cd9830054abb5d3edd89","tid":2034923,"uid":189068,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:35:12.000Z","msg":"男女平權！<br />\n點解停女未停男！？<br />\n男人條命就賤啲！？"},{"pid":"0f2b296eb85733cc0c445c4944ff021f2020e16e","tid":2034923,"uid":209773,"like":0,"disl